description: Unbeatable Value! Lowest Price Per Sq Ft for a 3-Bedroom Condo in South Boston! Live like it's a single family—with 2 full-size GARAGE parking spaces! This 3-level townhome on a quiet one-way street is significantly undervalued given its recent upgrades: brand-new hardwood floors throughout & a new central A/C system. The sunlit main level features an open layout w/ stainless steel appliances, granite counters, pantry, island, & 1/2 bath. The 2nd floor includes 2 spacious bedrooms, full bath, & in-unit laundry. Upstairs, the primary suite offers vaulted ceilings, a skylight, dual closets, an oversized en-suite bath & a bonus loft. While the bathrooms are functional, they are dated & present a great opportunity for the next owner to add value w/ cosmetic updates. Additional highlights: 2021 hot water tank, private patio, shared courtyard, professional management & a financially strong association. Minutes to Southie’s top dining, shopping, beaches, & public transit.
